cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.SI 

This paper is primarily focused on privacy-preserving techniques for POI recommendation, which falls under the category of security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a novel framework for POI recommendation that involves machine learning techniques such as Factorization Machines (cs.LG) and federated learning (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper deals with data management and storage (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in the context of POI recommendation.
